{"tid":1807111,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet 登告示牌榜首　橫掃海內外單週榜冠軍！","createTime":"2020-01-01T15:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T06:52:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c79cd4ba99680dfccaaef6deca2bf23ac75d61","tid":1807111,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:53:58.000Z","msg":"回歸滿一週的 Red Velvet 繼即時音源榜後也開始攻佔各種單週榜，甚至拿下告示牌榜的冠軍，恭喜她們！<br />\n<br />\n根據今天（1 日）更新的告示牌 World Digital Song Sales 榜顯示，Red Velvet 的最新主打歌 &ldquo;Psycho&rdquo; 成功空降冠軍寶座；除此之外，她們也連續兩週獲得 Social 50 榜的亞軍，是韓國女子團體史上的最佳紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n在這同時，&rdquo;Psycho&rdquo; 也拿下了韓國的 Genie、Bugs、Olleh Music、Soribada⋯⋯等網站的單週音源榜冠軍，海內外人氣都持續上升。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，SM Entertainment 昨晚也釋出了 Red Velvet 在耶誕夜舉行特別活動的影片，一起來重溫當時的氛圍，也希望 Wendy 早日康復！"},{"pid":"e816100ddcd23aa3c1296bcfe28cacdd46ba2af4","tid":1807111,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/15ae55fbcda8b81c239d8066f0d2ab80/79ee0d7eda58f39a-a6/s500x750/1373ec2c23eea095a3273f1570c6295f04020a18.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F15ae55fbcda8b81c239d8066f0d2ab80%2F79ee0d7eda58f39a-a6%2Fs500x750%2F1373ec2c23eea095a3273f1570c6295f04020a18.gifv&h=583fe9ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/063707adec6a00283334fc0801bff761/79ee0d7eda58f39a-ba/s500x750/cb50bec66c3cfe993f6586a3e7283144aa2cd286.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F063707adec6a00283334fc0801bff761%2F79ee0d7eda58f39a-ba%2Fs500x750%2Fcb50bec66c3cfe993f6586a3e7283144aa2cd286.gifv&h=c801a063&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"832965aa6de174e5c08deeb5a3ac5ca1d4f2c951","tid":1807111,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"Irene Joy Yeri Wendy 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea839d2ecfe15ce6c3127cdcb